    <!-- FAQ -->
    <section class="fade-in" style="background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.02);">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-header">
                <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-list">
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
                        <span>How does Calva's AI sound? Will customers know it's not human?</span>
                        <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
                    </button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Calva uses state-of-the-art voice synthesis that sounds remarkably human. Most callers can't tell the difference. The voice is natural, warm, and professional. Call (929) 755-7288 right now to hear it yourself—you'll be talking to Calva live.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
                        <span>How long does setup actually take?</span>
                        <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
                    </button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Most businesses are live in under 5 minutes. You choose your industry, customize your greeting, and start forwarding calls. Unlike human answering services that need days of training, Calva works immediately out of the box with pre-trained industry knowledge.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
                        <span>Can I use my existing phone number?</span>
                        <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
                    </button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Yes! Simply forward calls from your existing number to Calva. We can also provide a new local or toll-free number if you prefer. No hardware changes, no phone system upgrades required. It works with any carrier.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
                        <span>What happens if the AI can't answer a question?</span>
                        <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
                    </button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Calva is trained on your business info and FAQs, so it handles 95%+ of calls perfectly. If it encounters something new, it captures the question and caller details, then sends you an immediate SMS alert. You can also set transfer rules to route urgent calls directly to you or your team.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
                        <span>Does it integrate with my calendar and CRM?</span>
                        <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
                    </button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Yes. Calva integrates with Google Calendar, Outlook, Calendly, and most major calendar platforms. It checks your availability in real-time and books appointments directly with automatic confirmations. We also integrate with popular CRMs like Salesforce, HubSpot, and Zoho.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="faq-item">
                    <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
                        <span>Is there a contract or can I cancel anytime?</span>
                        <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
                    </button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>No contracts, ever. Cancel anytime with one click from your dashboard. We're confident you'll love Calva, which is why we keep it simple and flexible. Plus, we offer a 7-day free trial and a 30-day money-back guarantee on all plans.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="footer-content">
                <div class="footer-brand">
